<a href="#customer-spotlight" name="customer-spotlight"></a><table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" class="full-block" style="border-collapse:collapse; " ><tr ><td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" ><table cellpadding="40" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; " ><tr ><td align="left" valign="middle" class="text-block" style="padding-bottom:10px; color:#666666; font-size:13px; line-height:22px; " ><div class="mktEditable" id="customer-spotlight-title" style="padding-bottom:20px; " ><span style="margin:0; font-size:20px; font-weight:bold; line-height:24px; text-transform:uppercase;">Customer Spotlight</span><br></div>
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; " ><tr ><td align="left" valign="top" class="stack" style="color:#666666; font-size:14px; line-height:22px; padding-bottom:20px; " ><div class="mktEditable" id="customer-spotlight-entry" >
<p class="normal"><strong>Gemfire Advocates Launch Inaugural Customer Advisory Board<br /></strong>Pivotal customers from financial and airline sectors recently gathered in Palo Alto for the company's first-ever GemFire Customer Advisory Board (CAB) meeting.
    Representatives from <a style="color: #059a91; text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.broadridge.com/">Broadridge</a>, <a style="color: #059a91; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.cibc.com/">CIBC</a>, <a style="color: #059a91; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.southwest.com/">Southwest Airlines</a>, <a style="color: #059a91; text-decoration: none;" 
href="https://www.murex.com/">Murex</a>, and <a style="color: #059a91; text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.societegenerale.com/en/home">Societe Generale</a> spent the day discussing how each of their companies use GemFire, and how they&rsquo;d like to see the product evolve to best serve customers and compete in the market.
     <br /><br /> The newly-minted CAB members spent the following day at the first Geode Summit.
    In between their presentations to attendees, company representatives participated in on-camera interviews with Scott Yara.
    These conversations captured a unique take on how data is shaping their respective business and vertical.
    Stay on the lookout for these videos, which we&rsquo;ll roll out in the coming months.
    <br /><br /> If you have a customer story worth sharing, contact <a style="color: #059a91; text-decoration: none;" href="mailto:stseng@pivotal.io">Sophia Tseng</a> or <a style="color: #059a91; text-decoration: none;" href="mailto:ehayes@pivotal.io">Estelle Hayes</a>.<br /><br /> <img src="http://connect.pivotal.io/rs/625-IUJ-009/images/custspotlightv4n4.JPG" alt="CAB meeting" width="500" 
/><em><span style="font-size: 10px;">Brian Dunlap of Southwest Airlines and Andre Langevin of  CIBC compare notes during the first-ever Gemfire CAB meeting.</span></em></p>
